title: Dakine Carrie Shoulder Bag
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Carrie Shoulder Bag in our Jasmine print.
Carrie Features:
- Interior padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Vinyl trims and shoulder straps
- Adjustable and removable cross body shoulder strap
- Metal hardware
- Zippered closure
- Exterior zippered pocket
- Interior organizer pockets
- Nylon lining
- Black is Crinkle 420D nylon
